Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.16,0:00:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都有无数个梦想等待着被实现。\NEveryday there are millions of future waiting to be built.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,它们始于灵光一闪，\NEach one starts with a spark,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,或是受启发的一刻。\Na moment of inspiration,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,随着时间的推移愈发闪亮。\Nslowly going brighter over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,(别这样嘛...)\N(Come on...)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.92,0:00:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,(Cieo，派对要迟到了)\N(Hey Cleo, we're gonna be late for the party.)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,(就再等我一分钟！)\N(One minute!)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但当我们将想法分享，\NBut when we share our ideas,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.47,0:00:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一起工作，\Nand work together,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,面对共同的挑战，\Nto solve common challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,就会有神奇的事情发生。\NSomething amazing happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,（这些创造将）启发他人将其应用于新的领域、\NSomething that sparks others to create new applications,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(超赞！)\N(Awesome!)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,产生新的想法，\Nnew ideas,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,(你的儿子会没事的。)\N(Your son is going to be okay.)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,和超乎我们想象的新的创造。\Nnew innovations we can only begin to imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,解决那些我们无法独自解决的问题，\NSolving real problems larger than ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一起构建未来。\NBuilding the future, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你会构建什么样的未来？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,GitHub 构建未来(Building the Future) 宣传片\N[Outloudvi 译]
